    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>ABC Restaurant was established in 1990, with a mission to provide the finest dining experience in Sri Lanka. Over the years, we have expanded to multiple locations, offering a variety of cuisines and hospitality services that cater to all tastes and preferences.</p>

    <h2>Our Values</h2>
    <p>We believe in quality, customer satisfaction, and innovation. Our team is dedicated to creating memorable experiences for our customers by offering top-notch services, delicious food, and a warm atmosphere.</p>

    <h2>Our Services</h2>
    <p>From dine-in and delivery to catering for events, we provide a range of services to meet your needs. Our facilities include free Wi-Fi, private dining rooms, and special packages for events and parties.</p>

    <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
    <p>At ABC Restaurant, we are committed to excellence. Our chefs use the freshest ingredients to prepare each dish with care, and our staff is trained to provide the best service possible. Whether you're here for a meal, a celebration, or simply to enjoy our ambiance, we promise to make your visit worthwhile.</p>
